OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV starts search for
OL,4,Credundancies but Ofcom decision could
OL,5,Cbe months away
OL,6,
OL,7,FA trawl for volunteers for redundancy
OL,8,Fat STV was due to close on Friday.
OL,10,FThe firm is planning to cut about 60
OL,11,Fjobs including around 30 in news.
OL,13,FThe main cut the company is planning
OL,14,Fis, of course, the end of the news
OL,15,Fservice for the former Grampian region.
OL,17,FBut it will be several weeks - maybe
OL,18,Fmonths - before Ofcom decides whether
OL,19,Fto allow this.
