OL,4,Credundancies but Ofcom decision could
OL,5,Cbe months away
OL,6,
OL,7,FI'm not quite sure how any broadcaster
OL,8,Fcan reorganise its operations - or
OL,9,Fdecide whether it can make significant
OL,10,Fnumbers of news staff redundant -
OL,11,Fbefore it knows whether it will
OL,12,Factually be able to make changes to
OL,13,Foutput.
OL,15,FClearly it is possible Ofcom might
OL,16,Fblock the scheme completely, although
OL,17,Fthis is thought highly unlikely.
