OL,6,
OL,7,FStill it could insist on a separate
OL,8,Fnews service for the former Grampian
OL,9,Fregion remaining. Stranger things have
OL,10,Fhappened.
OL,12,FThis clearly would mean keeping a large
OL,13,Feditorial operation in Aberdeen and the
OL,14,Fnorth of Scotland.
OL,16,FStudio presentation and production can
OL,17,Fmove to Glasgow without Ofcom
OL,18,Fpermission.
