OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV starts search for
OL,4,Credundancies but Ofcom decision could
OL,5,Cbe months away
OL,6,
OL,7,FRealistically, if any dedicated output
OL,8,Ffor the north remained it would have to
OL,9,Fbe recorded.
OL,11,FMy own suspicion is that Ofcom will
OL,12,Feither approve STV's proposals -
OL,13,Fdespite huge political objections - or
OL,14,Finsist on a sub-opt for the north. Even
OL,15,Fdoing this could still save jobs.
OL,17,FIt is important to remember that STV's
OL,18,Fcurrent service includes both Scottish
OL,19,Fnational news and stories of local and
OL,20,Fregional interest.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
