OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV starts search for
OL,4,Credundancies but Ofcom decision could
OL,5,Cbe months away
OL,6,
OL,7,FAll the news programmes in the nations
OL,8,Fare very different editorially to
OL,9,FEnglish regional programmes.
OL,11,FSTV currently has one advantage over
OL,12,Fthe BBC - it can also cover the kind of
OL,13,Flocal and regional stories which are
OL,14,Funlikely to be seen on Reporting
OL,15,FScotland .
OL,17,FBut is it fair to impose an obligation
OL,18,Fon a commercial broadcaster to do
OL,19,Fsomething which the BBC has never done?
OL,21,FThis is not 1961 or even 1993.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
