OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV starts search for
OL,4,Credundancies but Ofcom decision could
OL,5,Cbe months away
OL,6,
OL,7,FOr does the simple fact that ratings
OL,8,Ffor STV North are good mean that taking
OL,9,Fthe axe to the service is a huge
OL,10,Fmisjudgement?
OL,12,FSTV points out that it's legal
OL,13,Fobligations are greater than those of
OL,14,FUTV and ITV Wales.
OL,16,FAgainst this are two obvious points.
OL,17,FScotland is bigger than Wales or
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland and has always been
OL,19,Fsplit into three channel 3 regions.
