OL,5,Cbe months away
OL,6,
OL,7,FAdd on changing consumer behaviour and
OL,8,Fyou can see that there is at least an
OL,9,Fargument - if not necessarily a
OL,10,Fcompelling case - for change.
OL,12,FThe actual boundary between STV's two
OL,13,Fregions merely reflects transmitter
OL,14,Fareas. It is not as simple as saying
OL,15,FAberdeen is different to Glasgow.
OL,17,FIt is for all those reasons that Ofcom
OL,18,Fmay face big questions if it does not
OL,19,Frun a lengthy, detailed consultation.
